Italian Soldier Killed, Other Hurt in Afghanistan Attack

-- B y   S o n i a   S i r l e t t i
-- 
2011-07-02T12:51:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-02/italian-soldier-killed-other-hurt-in-afghanistan-attack.html
One Italian soldier was killed and
another injured in an attack in  Afghanistan , Italian President
Giorgio Napolitano said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
